
INSTALL
=======

Requirements
------------

Install the following::

    apt-get install luarocks
    apt-get install liblua5.1-sql-postgres-dev

    apt-get install postgresql-server-dev-9.1
    sudo luarocks install luasql-postgres
    luarocks install lualogging
    luarocks install loop
    luarocks install md5
    luarocks install luafilesystem


Configure FreeSWITCH
--------------------

Edit autoload_configs/lua.conf.xml::

    <param name="module-directory" value="/usr/lib/x86_64-linux-gnu/?.so"/>
    <param name="module-directory" value="/usr/lib/x86_64-linux-gnu/lua/5.1/luasql/?.so"/>
    <param name="module-directory" value="/usr/lib/x86_64-linux-gnu/lua/5.1/luasql/postgres.so"/>

    <param name="script-directory" value="/home/areski/public_html/Lua/luaplay/FreeSWITCH/?lua"/>


Compile
-------
luac -o newfies.luac newfies.lua
